title: War of the Roses - It's a Flirting Work Relationship
description: Jess & Tim are dating and they both work at the same restaurant. Recently though, she started receiving really good shifts and he keeps getting stuck with bad shifts. This raises some suspicions because he thinks she's hooking up with the boss to get them.
